<figureCitation box="[279,345,295,320]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,250,1304,1326]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,267,1272]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[151,1436,267,1282]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. P 1 – P 6: present study specimen collection sites. B 1 – B 3: collection sites for Xestoleberis variegata and Xestoleberis curta by Brady (1890). Refer to Table 1 for site details. Color-coded circles indicating the geographical distribution of Fijian Xestoleberis species (seven new species described by the present paper and two species reported by Brady (1890 )). Ocean depth contours and the fast flowing Bligh Water currents are also illustrated." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/208331/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
